physical_examinations.vital_signs: Vital signs of the patient were within normal limits.
physical_examinations.relevant_findings: Progeroid appearance with frontal bossing, dysmorphic facies, micropthalmia with strabismus, long philtrum, wide anterior and posterior fontanels, low-set ears with large ear lobes, excessive skin folds over limbs, generalized hypotonia, flexion deformity of wrists, hyper-extensible metacarpophalangeal joints, clawing of hands, marked pectus excavatum, very thin and transparent skin over abdomen and thorax with visible veins, mild clitoromegaly, hypotelorism, bilateral corneal opacities, cataract formation, normal rooting and sucking reflexes, incomplete Moro's reflexes.
